The pattern for skills is as follows:

Filename should be skill name (Case sensitive)
In file:-

Skill Name
Description
Macro name (with respect to root_game_folder/data/macros)
Activation (0-On start of turn, 1-Just before attack, 2-End of Turn, 3-When Played, 4-When dead, 5-When opposite card dies,6-When taking attack damage,7-when taking magic damage,8-Just after attacking)
